CREATE TEMPORARY TABLE SalesTemp(
	OnlineSalesKey int not null
		primary key,
	SalesQuantity int null,
	SalesAmount float null,
	TotalCost float null,
	UnitCost float null,
	UnitPrice float null,
	CustomerLabel varchar(100) charset utf8 null,
	Title varchar(8) charset utf8 null,
	FirstName varchar(50) charset utf8 null,
	MiddleName varchar(50) charset utf8 null,
	LastName varchar(50) charset utf8 null,
	BirthDate date null,
	MaritalStatus varchar(1) charset utf8 null,
	Gender varchar(1) charset utf8 null,
	EmailAddress varchar(50) charset utf8 null,
	YearlyIncome float null,
	NumberChildrenAtHome tinyint null,
	TotalChildren tinyint null,
	Education varchar(40) charset utf8 null,
	Occupation varchar(100) charset utf8 null,
	HouseOwnerFlag char charset utf8 null,
	NumberCarsOwned tinyint null,
	AddressLine1 varchar(120) charset utf8 null,
	Phone varchar(20) charset utf8 null,
	CurrencyLabel varchar(10) charset utf8 null,
	CurrencyName varchar(20) charset utf8 null,
	CurrencyDescription varchar(50) charset utf8 null,
	IsWorkDay varchar(20) charset utf8 null,
	IsHoliday int null,
	HolidayName varchar(20) charset utf8 null,
	EuropeSeason varchar(50) charset utf8 null,
	NorthAmericaSeason varchar(50) charset utf8 null,
	AsiaSeason varchar(50) charset utf8 null,
	ProductLabel varchar(255) charset utf8 null,
	ProductName varchar(500) charset utf8 null,
	ProductDescription varchar(400) charset utf8 null,
	Manufacturer varchar(50) charset utf8 null,
	BrandName varchar(50) charset utf8 null,
	ColorName varchar(20) charset utf8 null,
	Size varchar(50) charset utf8 null,
	Weight float null,
	ProductCategoryLabel varchar(100) charset utf8 null,
	ProductCategoryName varchar(30) charset utf8 null,
	ProductCategoryDescription varchar(50) charset utf8 null,
	StoreManager int null,
	StoreType varchar(15) charset utf8 null,
	StoreName varchar(100) charset utf8 null,
	StoreDescription varchar(300) charset utf8 null,
	Status varchar(20) charset utf8 null,
	OpenDate datetime null,
	CloseDate datetime null,
	StorePhone varchar(15) charset utf8 null,
	StoreFax varchar(14) charset utf8 null,
	store_address varchar(100) charset utf8 null
);
